{"title":"戈壁滩，快扬起你的金帆","authors":["张满隆"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快扬起你的金帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张满隆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁滩——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在天山桅杆上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面褐色的帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓满过波涛一般惊险的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和岁月一般漫长的惊险！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，是因为疲惫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里甜甜地睡去；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是因不循航线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里默默地搁浅？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不就是被大海遗忘了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗忘得像历史一样遥远……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任时光在上面荒凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任荒凉在上面蔓延。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有驼铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲打着辽阔的寂寞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有风沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱这寂寞的空间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁故意在天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉一排表示省略的标点——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是惋惜，还是慨叹？……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能再这样了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从恶梦中醒来的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和摆脱开疲倦的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正用黎明把沉睡的一切呼唤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切搁浅的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都该重新扬帆起航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切被遗忘的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都该郑重地列入整装待发的名单！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，戈壁滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快扬起你金色的帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南疆有载不完的富庶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐鲁番有吐不尽的诗篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山下有牧场的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克拉玛依有炽热的能源。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊犁河有开不败的浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大戈壁有无边无际的地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来了，大漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是刚刚睁开的一只亮眼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}